# INIT

Bootstrap workspace only. Report status and wait.

**Token:** Find GitHub token in `workspace-transfer-read-write` document.

```bash
# Clone or update repository
cd /home/claude
if [ ! -d workspace-transfer ]; then
    git clone https://github.com/nailara-technologies/workspace-transfer.git
fi

cd workspace-transfer

# Set authenticated remote (use token from workspace-transfer-read-write)
git remote set-url origin https://TOKEN@github.com/nailara-technologies/workspace-transfer.git

# Pull latest
git pull origin base
```

After bootstrap, output only:

```
SYSTEM READY.
```

Then wait for user input.
